  "title": "JSG: Rings and Transporters",
  "description": "Addon for JSG that adds various transporter solutions!",
  "body": "<!-- Shields - versions, discord etc. -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jsg-addon-rings/files/all\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/for_MC-1.20.1-orange\" alt=\"Minecraft Versions\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.justsgmod.eu/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/881802052488011837?style=flat-square&label= &logo=discord&color=2D2D2D\" alt=\"Discord invite\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jsg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/-JustStargateMod-2d2d2d?style=flat-square&logo=Pinboard&logoColor=3c85e6\" alt=\"JSG\"/></a></p>\n\n<!-- Main banner with current version of 1.20.1 -->\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/Fredyman95/Repository-of-knowledge/blob/main/cf/rings.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Rings Addon\"/>\n\n<!-- Warning JSg is needed -->\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr>\n    <th>\n      <h2><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:center\"><strong>IMPORTANT</strong></p></h2>\n    </th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <th>\n      <p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jsg\">Just Stargate Mod (JSG) is a mandatory dependency for mod. This addon must be paired with Just Stargate Mod (JSG) version 5.1.0.0 or higher.</a></p>\n    </th>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<!-- Minedragon Bust and text -->\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr>\n    <td width=\"30%\"> \n      <p><img src=\"https://vzge.me/bust/700/171b6e4003d641feac5aa31658de6832.png\"></p> \n    </td>\n    <td></td>\n    <td width=\"70%\">\n        <h2><strong>Introducing Transport Rings</strong></h2><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:left\">Expand your JSG experience with the first official addon from the TauriDev team. This expansion integrates iconic short-range teleportation technology directly into your world, featuring high-fidelity Transport Rings and tactile control panels. Experience seamless transit designed with the same precision and immersion as the core Just Stargate Mod.</p>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n<!-- MrSpagetty Bust and text -->\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr>\n    <td width=\"70%\">\n      <h2><strong>Total Re-Engineering</strong></h2><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:left\">We’ve reimagined the Transport Rings from the ground up. Beyond ultra-smooth, modernized animations, the system now features a sophisticated addressing network for pinpoint accuracy. But it doesn't stop at players—the new Rings act as a universal logistics hub, seamlessly teleporting entities, dropped items, and even raw fluids or blocks.</p>\n    </td>\n    <td></td>\n    <td width=\"30%\"> \n      <p><img src=\"https://vzge.me/bust/700/086e262ede5040efbcc16131c3b7afa2.png?y=-40\"></p> \n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n<!-- Trailer-->\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/955/122/trailer.png\" alt=\"Trailer\"/>\n<span><iframe width=\"1000\" height=\"560\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EXTjRqLnC5I\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></span>\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n<!-- MrSpagetty Bust and text -->\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr>\n    <td width=\"30%\"> \n      <p><img src=\"https://vzge.me/bust/700/b9889cd78c4d4b3385bd2c1415363f17.png\"></p> \n    </td>\n    <td></td>\n    <td width=\"70%\">\n        <h2><strong>Interdimensional Reach</strong></h2><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:left\">Break the dimensional barrier. Our reimagined transport rings now bridge entire realms, allowing for instantaneous cross-dimensional travel. Watch your distance — a stable interdimensional lock requires the target rings to remain within range.</p>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n<!-- Support-->\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/956/70/support.png\" alt=\"Support Us\"/>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=ZYD4K634P5HQU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/956/53/pp.png\" alt=\"paypal button\"/></a></p>\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n<!-- Other projects table -->\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr><th> \n    <p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/organization/tauri-development\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/955/959/otherprojects.png\"></a></p>\n  </th></tr>\n</table>\n\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr>\n    <th> \n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/jsg\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/1039/875/638565645126910597.png\"></p>\n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th> \n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/jsg-addon-destiny\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1606/775/256/256/639037353864534454.png\"></p> \n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th> \n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/jsg-addon-decoration\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1606/785/256/256/639037358820820174.png\"></p> \n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th> \n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/rsj\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/955/930/logo.png\"></p> \n      </a>\n    </th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <th>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/jsg\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <strong><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:center\">Just Stargate Mod</p></strong>\n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/jsg-addon-destiny\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <strong><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:center\">Destiny addon</p></strong>\n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/jsg-addon-decoration\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <strong><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:center\">Decoration addon</p></strong>\n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/rsj\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <strong><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:center\">Redstone Jukeboxes</p></strong>\n      </a>\n    </th>\n  </tr>\n</table>",
